Songs from the Second Floor;;2000;;Not Rated;;Comedy,Drama;;7.6;;Roy Andersson;;Lars Nordh,Stefan Larsson,Bengt C.W. Carlsson,Torbjörn Fahlström,Sten Andersson,Rolando Núñez,Lucio Vucina,Per Jörnelius,Peter Roth,Klas-Gösta Olsson,Nils-Åke Eriksson,Hanna Eriksson,Tommy Johansson,Sture Olsson,Fredrik Sjögren,Stephen Whitton,Jöran Mueller,Eva Stenfelt;;A film poem inspired by the Peruvian poet César Vallejo. A story about our need for love, our confusion, greatness and smallness and, most of all, our vulnerability. It is a story with many characters, among them a father and his mistress, his youngest son and his girlfriend. It is a film about big lies, abandonment and the eternal longing for companionship and confirmation.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0120263/